--Aeon ACU Upgrades
Description['eal0001'] = "Houses Commander in a superior upgradeable suit with radar/sonar stealth, tac & torpedo deflection, and anti-teleport field. Contains all blueprints necessary to build a basic army. The AEON ACU is able to mount a variety of beam or artillery weapons, intel tools, shields and area-based defensive systems."

-- LEFT ARM tab --
Description['eal0001-exles1'] = "Improved Engineering unlocks T2 construction, improves build power, resources & mobility.       \n \n x3 Base Build Power  \n x2 Base Mass Production  \n x5 Base Energy Production                            \n +7% Movement "
Description['eal0001-exles2'] = "Advanced engineering unlocks T3 construction, more build power, resources, regen & mobility.    \n \n x9 Base Build Power  \n x5 Base Mass Production  \n x25 Base Energy Production \n x1.6 Base Regeneration \n +14% Movement"
Description['eal0001-exles3'] = "Superior engineering unlocks T4 construction, maximum build power, resources, regen & mobility. \n \n x16 Base Build Power \n x12 Base Mass Production \n x75 Base Energy Production \n x3.0 Base Regeneration \n +20% movement"

Description['eal0001-exlce1'] = "Combat Engineering unlocks T2 construction, with a focus on armor & regenerative capability. Mobility is slightly impaired.   \n \n x2.5 Base Build Power \n x1.30 HP from base value \n x1.6 Base Regeneration                                                           \n -4% Movement    \n Installs Chrono Dampener (Stun T1-T2 Duration 2)  "
Description['eal0001-exlce2'] = "Assault Engineering unlocks T3 construction, with more armor & regeneration & a small resource boost. Mobility is impaired.   \n \n x5.0 Base Build Power \n x1.75 HP from base value \n x3.0 Base Regeneration \n x2 Base Mass Production \n x5 Base Energy Production   \n -9% Movement    \n Chrono Dampener Range +8 (Stun T1-T3 Duration 2.5)"
Description['eal0001-exlce3'] = "Frontline Engineering unlocks T4 construction, maximum armor, regen, mild build power & resource gain, but Mobilty impaired.  \n \n x9.0 Base Build Power \n x2.20 HP from base value \n x4.5 Base Regeneration \n x5 Base Mass Production \n x25 Base Energy Production  \n -12.75% Movement " 

-- RIGHT ARM tab --
Description['eal0001-exrzb1'] = "Jury Rigged Disruptor\n Using parallel energy feeds & capacitors, allows an enhanced main weapon but slightly slows mobility. \n \n x1.5 Base Damage \n +5 Range \n +5 Overcharge Range \n -4% Movement"

Description['eal0001-exrtorp1'] = "When forced to fight underwater, a basic heavy torpedo system is an absolute necessity.                                         \n \n Installs Torpedo Launcher    \n 380 torpedo damage \n 2 torpedoes per salvo \n 60 range"
Description['eal0001-exrtorp2'] = "An improved reloader increases the torpedo salvo size using lighter, but longer ranged, torpedoes.                                                              \n \n 250 torpedo damage \n 4 torpedoes per salvo \n 66 range"
Description['eal0001-exrtorp3'] = "An added tube, plasma impellors & shaped charges, increases the salvo size, range & damage of the system. Mobility reduced.                                     \n \n 300 torpedo damage \n 5 torpedoes per salvo \n 72 range \n +33% torpedo velocity \n -4% Movement"

Description['eal0001-exramc1'] = "Miasma artillery uses shells containing corrosive materials that cause damage over a short period of time over an area. Excellent in range, accuracy is low.   \n \n 100 Range \n 144 Damage \n 2.0 AOE Radius "
Description['eal0001-exramc2'] = "Using molecular compression, it becomes possible to condense the corrosive materials into a extremely dense state - increases range, damage, AOE & Accuracy.   \n \n 112 range \n 250 damage \n 2.5 AOE Radius \n +5% Accuracy "
Description['eal0001-exramc3'] = "Creating the warheads in the tube, prior to firing, allows for denser warheads to be delivered at an increased speed, without making the weapon heavier.       \n \n 124 range \n 428 damage \n 2.9 AOE Radius \n +15% Accuracy "

Description['eal0001-exrgec1'] = "Phason Beam Cannon \n The standard Aeon Phason Beam cannon, augments the existing Disruptor.                             \n \n 210 Damage \n 38 Range"
Description['eal0001-exrgec2'] = "Tri-Channel Booster\n Installs backup emitters that alternate, preventing thermal shutdown, increasing range & damage.   \n \n 420 Damage \n 46 Range                                   \n Installs Chrono Dampener (Stun T1-T2 Duration 2)"
Description['eal0001-exrgec3'] = "Pulsing the wave in specific bursts creates local feedback at the target, creating blast events. Impairs mobility.       \n \n 630 Damage \n 55 Range \n 2.5 AOE Radius \n -4% Movement \n Chrono Dampener Range +8 (Stun T1-T3 Duration 2.5)"

-- COMMAND tab --
Description['eal0001-excint1'] = "Intel Enhancement T2\n Intel is always a priority for effective command. An ACU with a need to know requires increased vision as well as increased radar & sonar.   \n \n Installs T2 intel package  \n x1.25 Base Vision & Water Vision Radius \n x2.5 Base Radar Radius \n x2 Base Sonar Radius"
Description['eal0001-excint2'] = "Intel Enhancement T3\n The road to victory starts with good intel, which means a need for even more vision, radar, OMNI & sonar.                                    \n \n Installs T3 OMNI package   \n x1.75 Base Vision & Water Vision Radius \n x5.0 Base Radar Radius \n x4 Base Sonar Radius \n x4 Base OMNI Radius "
Description['eal0001-excint3'] = "Rhianne Intelligence Device, this cut-down version will teleport an optical device directly over a location. Requires manual activation. Uses no additional energy. \n \n Installs Optical Scry System "

-- BACK tab --
Description['eal0001-exbbat1'] = "Maelstrom Generator \n The Miasma effect creates a field corrosive to enemy units & acts as a radar/sonar Stealth Field.  \n \n 40 Damage  \n 24 Range         \n Radar & Sonar Stealth Field"
Description['eal0001-exbbat2'] = "Installing multiple emitters with detuned phasing, increases the range & effect of the Maelstrom Generator.               \n \n 75 Damage  \n 32 Range                 "
Description['eal0001-exbbat3'] = "Quantum manipulated focusers & reflectors further increases the range & effect of the Generator but impairs mobility.     \n \n 100 Damage \n 40 Range  \n -4% Movement"

Description['eal0001-exbtele'] = "Personal Teleporter\n Installs a back-mounted personal teleporter which allows jumps of several kilometres.\n\n Installs Teleporter"

Description['eal0001-exbsh1'] = "Shield Bubble \n A standard, inexpensive T2 level Shield Bubble.                                              \n \n 8500 Shield  \n 98 Regen"
Description['eal0001-exbsh2'] = "Replacing the bubble shield with a custom, T3 level, 'skin' shield, permits higher regeneration & strength.   \n \n 18000 Shield \n 187 Regen"
Description['eal0001-exbsh3'] = "The most advanced skin shielding possible on a unit but impairs mobility.                                     \n \n 28800 Shield \n 255 Regen \n -4% Movement"


-- UEF ACU Upgrades
Description['eel0001'] = "Houses Commander in a superior upgradeable suit with radar/sonar stealth, tac & torpedo deflection, and anti-teleport field. Contains all blueprints necessary to build a basic army from scratch. The UEF ACU is designed to carry an outstanding array of weapon and missile systems, intel tools and shield options"

-- LEFT ARM tab --
Description['eel0001-exles1'] = "Improved Engineering unlocks T2 construction, improves build power, resources & mobility.     \n \n x3 Base Build Power  \n x2 Base Mass Production  \n x5 Base Energy Production                            \n +7% Movement    \n Installs AA Lance"
Description['eel0001-exles2'] = "Advanced engineering unlocks T3 construction, more build power, resource, mobility & regen.   \n \n x9 Base Build Power  \n x5 Base Mass Production  \n x25 Base Energy Production \n x1.6 Base Regeneration \n +14% Movement                         "
Description['eel0001-exles3'] = "Superior engineering unlocks T4 construction, maximum build power, resource, mobility & regen.\n \n x16 Base Build Power \n x12 Base Mass Production \n x75 Base Energy Production \n x3.0 Base Regeneration \n +20% movement   \n Installs 2nd AA Lance"

Description['eel0001-exlce1'] = "Combat Engineering unlocks T2 construction, with a focus on armor & regenerative capability. Mobility is slightly impaired.  \n \n x2.5 Base Build Power \n x1.30 HP from base value \n x1.6 Base Regeneration                                                          \n -4% Movement       \n Installs Flamer \n 22 Range \n 120 Damage \n 2.0 AOE Radius "
Description['eel0001-exlce2'] = "Assault Engineering unlocks T3 construction, with more armor & regeneration & a small resource boost. Mobility is impaired.  \n \n x5.0 Base Build Power \n x1.75 HP from base value \n x3.0 Base Regeneration \n x2 Base Mass Production \n x5 Base Energy Production  \n -9% Movement                          \n 30 Range \n 180 Damage \n 2.5 AOE Radius "
Description['eel0001-exlce3'] = "Frontline Engineering unlocks T4 construction, maximum armor, regen, mild build power & resource gain, but Mobilty impaired. \n \n x9.0 Base Build Power \n x2.20 HP from base value \n x4.5 Base Regeneration \n x5 Base Mass Production \n x25 Base Energy Production \n -12.75% Movement "

-- RIGHT ARM tab --
Description['eel0001-exrzb1'] = "Jury Rigged Zephyr\n Coupling the ACU reactor directly to the weapon increases damage. Crude & Heavy, but inexpensive  \n \n x1.5 Base Damage \n +5 Range \n +5 Overcharge Range \n -4% Movement"

Description['eel0001-exrtorp1'] = "When forced to fight underwater, a basic heavy torpedo system is an absolute necessity.                                         \n \n Installs Torpedo Launcher    \n 380 torpedo damage \n 2 torpedoes per salvo \n 60 range"
Description['eel0001-exrtorp2'] = "An improved reloader increases the torpedo salvo size using lighter, but longer ranged, torpedoes.                                                              \n \n 250 torpedo damage \n 4 torpedoes per salvo \n 66 range"
Description['eel0001-exrtorp3'] = "An added tube, plasma impellors & shaped charges, increases the salvo size, range & damage of the system. Mobility reduced.                                     \n \n 300 torpedo damage \n 5 torpedoes per salvo \n 72 range \n +33% torpedo velocity \n -4% Movement"

Description['eel0001-exramc1'] = "Anti-Matter Cannon\n A very powerful but short range blast cannon with a large AOE. Disables the standard Zephyr weapon.  \n \n 270 Damage \n 30 Range \n 3.0 AOE Radius"
Description['eel0001-exramc2'] = "An efficient particle accelerator makes it possible to impel more plasma, and thus denser plugs. Zephyr reactivated.      \n \n 390 Damage \n 36 Range \n 3.3 AOE Radius"
Description['eel0001-exramc3'] = "Magnetic constrictors reinforce the plasma wall, allowing higher density & powerful blast effects. Impairs mobility.      \n \n 750 Damage \n 42 Range \n 4.0 AOE Radius  \n 2 Second AOE Stun on T1, T2 & T3 \n -4% Movement"

Description['eel0001-exrgec1'] = "Growler Gatling Cannon\n Mounting the Growler gatling system alongside the Zephyr gives the ACU serious crowd-control firepower.                                     \n \n Installs Growler Gatling Cannon  \n 160 Damage \n 38 Range"
Description['eel0001-exrgec2'] = "Ravager Gatling AutoCannon\n The Ravager gatling system is a substantial increase in firepower & range. The Basic Flamer is also installed                           \n \n Installs Ravager Gatling Cannon  \n 305 Damage \n 56 Range                  \n \n Installs Flamer \n 22 Range \n 120 Damage \n 2.0 AOE Radius"
Description['eel0001-exrgec3'] = "Devastation AutoBlaster\n Hardened projectiles fire slower but inflict terrible kinetic impacts on targets. This Flamer is upgraded, but mobility is impaired.       \n \n Installs Devastation Autoblaster \n 440 Damage \n 62 Range \n 1 AOE Radius  \n \n Upgraded Flamer \n 30 Range \n 180 Damage \n 2.5 AOE Radius \n -4% Movement"

-- COMMAND tab --
Description['eel0001-excint1'] = "Intel Enhancement T2\n Intel is always a priority for effective command. An ACU with a need to know requires increased vision as well as increased radar & sonar.   \n \n Installs T2 intel package  \n x1.25 Base Vision & Water Vision Radius \n x2.5 Base Radar Radius \n x2 Base Sonar Radius"
Description['eel0001-excint2'] = "Intel Enhancement T3\n The road to victory starts with good intel, which means a need for even more vision, radar, OMNI & sonar.                                    \n \n Installs T3 OMNI package   \n x1.75 Base Vision & Water Vision Radius \n x5.0 Base Radar Radius \n x4 Base Sonar Radius \n x4 Base OMNI Radius "
Description['eel0001-excint3'] = "Recon Satellite\n Staying ahead of the flow of battle is necessary for success. This system uses a small remote spy satellite with simple vision capabilities. Satellite is maintained with power.\n\n Installs Recon Satellite"

-- BACK tab --
Description['eel0001-exbbat1'] = "Flapjack Missile Pack\n Firing a salvo of 6 Flapjack warheads, this gives a basic bombardment ability to the ACU.                   \n \n Installs Flapjack Missile Cluster  \n 180 Damage \n 1.5 AOE Radius \n 75 Range"
Description['eel0001-exbbat2'] = "Spearhead Missile Pack\n Bigger missiles, increased range, velocity and AOE.                                                        \n \n Installs Spearhead Missile Cluster \n 360 Damage \n 2.0 AOE Radius \n 88 Range"
Description['eel0001-exbbat3'] = "Fractal Missile Cluster\n Missiles which split into 3 warheads deliver more payload, more range & AOE, but at the cost of mobility. \n \n Installs Fractal Missiles Cluster  \n 468 Damage \n 2.6 AOE Radius \n 97 Range \n -4% Movement"

Description['eel0001-exbtele'] = "Personal Teleporter\n Installs a back-mounted personal teleporter which allows jumps of several kilometres.\n\n Installs Teleporter"

Description['eel0001-exbsh1'] = "Bubble Shield\n A standard, inexpensive T2 level Bubble Shield.                                                                                    \n \n 8500 Shield HP  \n 98 Shield Regen"
Description['eel0001-exbsh2'] = "Replacing the bubble shield with a custom, T3 level, 'skin' shield, permits higher regeneration & strength.                                        \n \n 16000 Shield HP \n 181 Shield Regen"
Description['eel0001-exbsh3'] = "Using the finest construction techniques allows a very advanced skin shielding.                                                                    \n \n 18750 Shield HP \n 308 Shield Regen"
Description['eel0001-exbsh4'] = "Typhoon Bubble Shield\n The most advanced mobile Bubble shield possible.                                      \n \n Installs Typhoon Bubble Shield \n 40000 Shield HP \n 288 Shield Regen"

Description['eel0001-exbtac1'] = "Tactical Missile System\n The ACU can install a standard tactical missile launcher on its chassis that allows for precise targeting at extreme range. This ability comes at the cost of decreased mobility.\n\n Installs Tactical Missile System\n Requires Ammo\n Manual Launch\n 6000 Damage\n 2 AOE Radius\n 256 Range\n x0.96 Speed\n x0.96 Acceleration\n x0.96 Turn Rate"
Description['eel0001-exbtac2'] = "Tactical Nuclear System\n The \"Billy Nuke\" system replaces the standard payload with nuclear-tipped warheads, bringing low-end weapons of mass destruction to the battlefield. This payload comes at the cost of a further reduction in mobility.\n\n Installs Tactical Nuclear Missiles\n 12000-250 Damage\n 15-25 Radius\n 256 Range\n x0.96 Speed\n x0.96 Acceleration\n x0.96 Turn Rate"


-- Cybran ACU Upgrades
Description['erl0001'] = "Houses Commander in a superior upgradeable suit with radar/sonar stealth, Torpedo/Tactical Missile defense & anti-teleport field. Contains blueprints necessary to build a basic army. Able to mount some potent, and unique, but shorter ranged weapons systems, the Cybran ACU's mobility, intel & counter-intel options make him hard to find"

-- LEFT ARM tab --
Description['erl0001-exles1'] = "Improved Engineering unlocks T2 construction, improves build power, resources & mobility.     \n \n Build Power x3 from base value  \n Mass Production x2 from base value  \n Energy Production x5 from base value  \n +7% Movement"
Description['erl0001-exles2'] = "Advanced engineering unlocks T3 construction, more build power, resource, mobility & regen.   \n \n Build Power x9 from base value  \n Mass Production x5 from base value  \n Energy Production x25 from base value \n +14% Movement \n Regen +60% from base value "
Description['erl0001-exles3'] = "Superior engineering unlocks T4 construction, maximum build power, resource, mobility & regen.\n \n Build Power x16 from base value \n Mass Production x12 from base value \n Energy Production x75 from base value \n +20% movement \n Regen x3 from base value \n Installs basic Rocket Pod"

Description['erl0001-exlce1'] = "Combat Engineering unlocks T2 construction, with a focus on armor & regenerative capability. Mobility is slightly impaired. \n \n Build Power x2.5 from base value \n x1.3 HP from base value  \n Regen x1.6 from base value \n -4% Movement"
Description['erl0001-exlce2'] = "Assault Engineering unlocks T3 construction, with more armor & regeneration & a small resource boost. Mobility is impaired. \n \n Build Power x5 from base value   \n x1.75 HP from base value \n Regen x3 from base value   \n -9% Movement     \n Mass Production x2 from base value \n Energy Production x5 from base value  \n Installs basic Rocket Pod "
Description['erl0001-exlce3'] = "Frontline Engineering unlocks T4 construction, maximum armor, regen, mild build power & resource gain, but Mobilty impaired.\n \n Build Power x9 from base value   \n x2.2 HP from base value  \n Regen x4.5 from base value \n -12.75% Movement \n Mass Production x5 from base value \n Energy Production x25 from base value \n Rocket Pod +8 range, +100% damage, +50% AOE range"

-- RIGHT ARM tab --
Description['erl0001-exrzb1'] = "Jury Rigged Ripper\n By running additional power feeds and rapidly upgrading capacitors, upgrading the command chassis with a slightly enhanced main weapon can be useful when in a pinch.\n\n x1.5 Base Damage\n +5 Range\n x0.96 Speed\n x0.96 Acceleration\n x0.96 Turn Rate\n +5 Overcharge Range"

Description['erl0001-exrtorp1'] = "Torpedo Launcher \n When forced to fight underwater, a basic heavy torpedo system is a necessity. \n Installs Torpedo Launcher"
Description['erl0001-exrtorp2'] = "An improved reloader increases the torpedo salvo size using lighter but longer ranged torpedoes. \n \n +6 Range \n +2 torpedo per salvo"
Description['erl0001-exrtorp3'] = "An added tube, plasma impellors and shaped charges, increases the salvo size, range & damage of the system. Mobility is slightly reduced.\n \n +6 range \n +1 torpedo per salvo \n +33% torpedo velocity \n -4% mobility"

Description['erl0001-exramc1'] = "EMP Blast Array\n Using AEON chrono tech, this weapon delivers a stunning blast of direct damage, and a sizable secondary stun blast against T1 & T2 units.\n\n Installs EMP Array\n 300 Damage\n 2 AOE Radius\n 35 Range\n 2 Second Stun on T1 & T2\n 4 Stun Radius"
Description['erl0001-exramc2'] = "Crystal Focusing\n Again, using SERAPHIM tech, focus crystals are improved, allowing the beams increased range, charge and AOE effects. Stuns T1-T3 units.\n\n 500 Damage\n 40 Range\n 2 Second Stun on T1, T2 & T3\n 5 Stun Radius"
Description['erl0001-exramc3'] = "Superior Hardware\n Built to rigorous UEF materiel standards, the lasers & conduits are completely replaced, allowing the ultimate form of this unique blast weapon. Stuns ALL land units. This tremendous package comes at the expense of ACU mobility.\n\n 800 Damage\n 3 AOE Radius\n 45 Range\n 3 Second Stun on ALL units\n 6 Stun Radius\n x0.96 Speed\n x0.96 Acceleration\n x0.96 Turn Rate"

Description['erl0001-exrgec1'] = "Microwave Laser\n The Microwave Laser or \"Maser\" for short, is a focused microwave beam with good damage but short range.\n\n Installs Microwave Laser\n 240 Damage\n 30 Range\n x1.1 Shield Damage"
Description['erl0001-exrgec2'] = "Beholder Assembly\n This pairs the original maser with a paralleled twin. While not noticeable to those viewing the system in action, it helps ensure higher power settings can be run while reducing maintenance demands caused by a single coil overheating.\n\n 360 Damage\n 34 Range\n x1.2 Shield Damage"
Description['erl0001-exrgec3'] = "Death Ray Conduits\n By running additional feeds directly to the main power systems, it is possible to overcharge the laser assembly and bring out the weapon's extremely destructive aspects. At these higher power levels, the system simply melts the armor off the target and flash fries their electronics. This overwhelmingly destructive power reduces mobility of the ACU.\n\n 600 Damage\n 40 Range\n x1.4 Shield Damage\n x0.96 Speed\n x0.96 Acceleration\n x0.96 Turn Rate"

-- COMMAND tab --
Description['erl0001-excint1'] = "Intel Enhancement T2\n Intel is always a priority for effective command. An ACU with a need to know requires increased vision as well as increased radar & sonar capabilities.\n\n Installs Mobile T2 intel package\n x1.25 Base Vision & Water Vision Radius\n x2.5 Base Radar Radius\n x2 Base Sonar Radius\n No OMNI enhancement"
Description['erl0001-excint2'] = "Intel Enhancement T3\n The road to victory starts with good intel, which means a need for even more vision, radar, OMNI & sonar.\n\n Installs Mobile T3 OMNI intel package\n x1.75 Base Vision & Water Vision Radius\n x5 Base Radar Radius\n x4 Base OMNI Radius\n x4 Base Sonar Radius"
Description['erl0001-excint3'] = "Perimeter Optics\n Utilizing SERAPHIM crystal technology, in conjunction with the existing OMNI radar, makes it possible to improve the visual intel of the ACU. Consumes additional power.\n\n +25 to base Vision & Water Vision Range"

-- BACK tab --
Description['erl0001-exbtele'] = "Personal Teleporter\n Installs a back-mounted personal teleporter which allows jumps of several kilometres.\n\n Installs Teleporter"

Description['erl0001-exbagile'] = "Agility Package\n By installing fine-tuned and highly responsive servos and actuators, it is possible for the command chassis to be more agile. While not faster, its acceleration is markedly improved, increasing overall mobility.\n\n x1.33 Acceleration\n x1.33 Turn Speed"
Description['erl0001-exbarmor'] = "Armor Package\n Simply adds framework for up to 7k of additional armor which must then be regenerated to obtain the full value. Mobility is impaired.\n\n +7000 HP\n x0.96 Speed\n x0.96 Acceleration\n x0.96 Turn Rate"
Description['erl0001-exbregen'] = "Regen Package\n A large cache of nanobots and a mass reserve increases the base regeneration of the ACU by 10.\n\n +10 Base Regen"

Description['erl0001-exbstealth'] = "Stealth Field\n Good intel can win the battle; however, so can depriving the enemy of intel. Augments the basic stealth capability of the ACU by mounting a typical radar/sonar stealth field generator.\n\n Installs T3 Radar/Sonar Stealth Field\n 32 Radar Stealth Field Radius\n 32 Sonar Stealth Field Radius"
Description['erl0001-exbcloak'] = "Cloak Armor\n A further upgrade to the Stealth Field Generator, it is possible to create the illusion of invisibility, applying a special active compound to the entire ACU frame which fools optical sensors.\n\n Installs Personal Cloaking\n Deactivated if the Stealth Field is turned off\n Increased power consumption even when turned off or deactivated"
Description['erl0001-exbdeviate'] = "Deviator Field\n Deviator Fields create EMP like effects at ranges beyond the stealth field itself, which interfere with all enemy intel collection thereby reducing the range of all enemy Radar/OMNI/Sonar/Vision & Water Vision devices.\n\n Installs Deviator Field Generator\n x0.8 Vision Radius\n x0.7 Radar Radius\n x0.6 OMNI Radius\n x0.7 Sonar Radius\n 80 Range\n Deactivated if the Stealth Field is turned off\n Increased power consumption even when turned off or deactivated"


